messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I pray for the deliverance from the spirit of lust I yield the lust of the eyes and the lust of the flesh and the pride of life to Jesus I pray for my wife's healing from the heart that I have caused her I pray for deliverance from the stronghold of fornication and adultery and harlotry and pornography and masturbation I pray that God would sweep through my soul and take out all the sexual sin I pray that he would drive Satan out of all the rebellious areas of my heart that was yielded to sexual sin I pray that in its place that he will place renewed purity holiness and wholeness and a spirit of obedience and remove the hardness of heart caused my sexual sin I pray for complete healing and and joy for my wife I pray he goes into our house and have his way with healing wholeness restoration joy and peace I pray for the renewed ones and happiness in our marriage
